Invocation Name: my annual pass status
des:
This skill let's you know if you can go to Disneyland park on the current day based on your type of annual pass. Only requirement is to tell Alexa what kind of pass you have and you'll be told if you can visit the park or not.

This skill is in no way affiliated with The Walt Disney Company, Disney World, Disneyland, or any of its subsidiaries
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
